	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
Their past was a nightmare. For many refugees, the Dream Center offers hope.									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>After the standard 90 days of federal assistance ends, many refugees in the U.S. are still finding their footing. Founded by refugees, the Dream Center offers support and compassion – and for many, a sense of family.&nbsp;</p>				</div>
			</div>
