    window.open(url,'_blank');
  });
});
</script>
	</div>	</div></div><p>Combined with travel bans targeting African countries that clients may pass through on their way to the U.S., Ms. Jallow says the government has effectively stopped the flow of refugees into the U.S. In the meantime, the Dream Center focuses on improving the lives of its clients. Ms. Jallow hopes that one day, they stop needing the center.</p><p>“I want to see them move forward,” she says, “get jobs, know English, be able to do things for themselves.”</p>

							</div> 
						</div>
					</div>
